      "lang": "zh",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "Sheep is a strategy puzzle video game released for PlayStation, Microsoft Windows and Game Boy Advance. In 2001 it was released for Mac OS X by Feral Interactive. The Game Boy Advance version was released in March 2002 in the EU, while the intended North American release was cancelled for unknown reasons.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "《绵羊传奇》（英語：Sheep）是一款2000年发行的策略益智类单人电子游戏。游戏由英国游戏开发商 Minds Eye Productions 制作，并由 Empire Interactive 等公司发行。玩家需要通过控制一名牧羊人角色将羊群赶往目的地，途中需要控制羊群来避免各种危险。游戏最后会根据通关时间和剩余羊群数量来计算分数。",
      "lang": "zh",
      "source": "wikipedia_zh"
    },
    {
      "text": "Sheep est un jeu vidéo de réflexion développé par Minds Eye Productions et édité par Empire Interactive, sorti en 2000 sur PlayStation et Windows. Des versions Game Boy Advance et Mac OS ont aussi vu le jour.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Sheep è un videogioco rompicapo sviluppato da Mind's Eye Productions e pubblicato nel 2000 da Empire Interactive per Windows, PlayStation e Game Boy Advance. La versione per Mac OS è stata distribuita da Feral Interactive. Il gioco è stato successivamente distribuito attraverso download digitale da PlayStation Store per PlayStation 3 e PSP.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    }
  ]
